text: Heteroclytomorpha punctata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Charles Joseph Gahan in 1888. It is known from the Solomon Islands.BioLib.cz - Heteroclytomorpha punctata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1888
